      • doneReading

        public boolean doneReading​(int total,
                           int curr)
        Given this configuration, determine if the messages read so far (curr) is at the total available or if config specified a max read count, then if curr > max read, return true.
        Parameters:
        total - total available.
        curr - current incrementor.
        Returns:
        true if client/session is done reading available msgs
